{"word":"G2435 - ἱλαστήριον - hilastḗrion - hil-as-tay'-ree-on - Mercyseat","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱλαστήριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hilastḗrion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hil-as-tay'-ree-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Mercyseat</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"கிருபாதார பலி, கிருபாசனம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. the well - known cover of the ark of the covenant in the Holy of holies"},{"paragraph":"2. an expiatory sacrifice"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2433 - ἱλάσκομαι - hiláskomai - hil-as'-kom-ahee/2433\">G2433</a>; an <i>expiatory</i> (place or thing), that is, (concretely) an atoning <i>victim</i>, or (specifically) the <i>lid</i> of the Ark (in the Temple): - mercyseat, propitiation.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2433/2433\">G2433</a>, <a href=\"#/G2434/2434\">G2434</a>, <a href=\"#/G2435/2435\">G2435</a>, <a href=\"#/G2436/2436\">G2436</a>"}]}